{
  "stem": "14613.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The same way-- like it is a revolution in the last 50 years in the-- in science, in communication.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean, what exists today, you could only dream about it 50 years ago.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then you were just a dreamer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Between Lodz and Warsaw, by and large, it was railroad.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Cars were very seldom used.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And very few people had cars.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So that railroad was the most commonly used between Lodz and Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The, the countryside basically looked like the word says-- 'countryside.' It was a country.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a lot of small villages scattered around.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You had great fields of-- which the peasants cultivated, so that you had a lot of corn and wheat and potatoes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was, by and large, the countryside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You did not have industrial sections coming from Lodz to, to Warsaw, like we have here from New York to, to Washington.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was mostly open fields.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, when you ask me this question today, and you ask me to look back 60 years, I, I would have to tell you whether Lodz or Warsaw was for me tremendous cities.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Yet, when I went back there, maybe 30 years later after the war, and I went to Lodz and to Warsaw, I thought to myself, is this the big city that I thought it was 50 years ago?",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It is like a miniature in comparison to the cities that I have seen already.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And therefore, the memories are, are-- going back, the memories are that it was tremendous.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But yet, it was small.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "On the other hand, however, we cannot forget that Lodz did have about 600,000 people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it was a large city.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I began school really, at young age.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
